chapter-6

DOM (part-1)
-----------------------

DOM manipulation-

select with id --  document.getElementByid("myId")

select with class -- document.getElementByClassName("myClass")

select with tag -- document.getElementByTagName("p")



Query selector 
---------------

document.querySelector("myId / myClass /tag )
//returns first element

document.querySelectorAll("myId / myClass /tag")
//returns a Nodelist


Properties :
-------------

tagName : returns tag for element nodes

innerText : returns the text content of the element and all its children

innerHTML : returns the plain text or HTML contents in the elements

textContent : returns textual content even for hidden elements


